---
source: protocol/tests/wire_stability.rs
expression: out
---
PROTOCOL_VERSION = 7

== Frame variants (discriminant = first byte; append at END) ==
Hello            00 01 06
SpanStart        01 01 02 03 04 05 06
SpanEnd          02 01 02
Event            03 01 02 03
Metric           04 01 03 03 04
Dropped          05 07
StringRegister   06 01 01 78
MetricRegister   07 01 01 02
ThreadRegister   08 01 01 74 02
ContextSwitch    09 01 02 03 01 04
HartRegister     0a 01 02 01
CapEvent         0b 01 01 02 03 02 04 05 06 07 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00
SyscallRefused   0c 01 07 02 03 04
Log              0d 01 6c 01 02 03
Message          0e 01 02 03 04 05 06
NotifySignal     0f 01 02 03 04 05
NotifyWait       10 01 02 03 04 05

== Supporting enums (arm = discriminant byte; append at END) ==
CapEventKind::Granted        00
CapEventKind::Transferred    01
CapEventKind::Revoked        02
CapEventKind::Minted         03
CapObject::TelemetrySink     00
CapObject::SpanSink          01
CapObject::Endpoint          02
CapObject::Reply             03
CapObject::Notification      04
CapObject::Process           05
SwitchReason::Yield          00
SwitchReason::Preempt        01
SwitchReason::Blocked        02
SwitchReason::Exit           03
MetricKind::Counter          00
MetricKind::Gauge            01
MetricKind::Histogram        02
HartRole::Boot               00
HartRole::Worker             01
RefusalReason::UnknownSyscall 00
RefusalReason::NoProcess     01
RefusalReason::CapNotFound   02
RefusalReason::CapWrongRights 03
RefusalReason::CapWrongObject 04
RefusalReason::BadUserRange  05
RefusalReason::BadUtf8       06
RefusalReason::Quota         07
RefusalReason::BadSpanId     08
RefusalReason::OutOfMemory   09
RefusalReason::UnknownProgram 0a
RefusalReason::BadMetricHandle 0b
RefusalReason::BadMetricKind 0c
RefusalReason::NotificationBusy 0d
RefusalReason::CapNotDelegable 0e
